Class EventMessageThreadsDeleted

  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    IEvent<Void>, IJobEvent<JobDeleteMessageThreads,Void>

    public class EventMessageThreadsDeleted
extends BaseJobEvent<JobDeleteMessageThreads,Void>
    Event published on the IEventBus (as returned by ServiceSupport.getEventBus()) once all users messageThreads are deleted. BaseJobEvent.getFailure() will return a null on success, on failure a non-null throwable.
    To delete all users messageThreads use JobDeleteMessageThreads
